  "rule_text": "Primary CTA buttons use Brand Blue #00529b background, White #ffffff text, Nunito Sans Bold 16px, padding 14px 32px, minimum 48px clickable touch-target height (brand accessibility rule: \u226548px clickable areas), and a fully rounded 24px pill radius echoing the rounded brand aesthetic. Secondary CTA uses a White background with a 2px Brand Blue border and Brand Blue text at the same metrics.",
